ngram\": \"security guards\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"high alert\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers and government officials have taken what they call a \\\"zero risk\\\" approach, with the largest deployment of security personnel in peacetime in French history.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 539, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"government officials\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"zero risk\\\" approach\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 471}, {\"ngram\": \"the largest deployment\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"security personnel\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"peacetime\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is estimated that the security cost could well exceed the \\u00a31billion spent on London 2012.\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999131433, \"rank\": 8.120365180909038e-11, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the security cost\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 44,000 metal barriers have been erected along the banks of the Seine,where a lavish and unprecedented opening ceremonywill take place.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999976866319613, \"rank\": 2.3132581366354095e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A total\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"44,000 metal barriers\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"a lavish and unprecedented opening ceremonywill\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Residents of certain areas of the city have required QR codes just to access their homes.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Residents\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"certain areas\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"QR codes\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under the codename Operation Sentinelle, a military base has been built on the outskirts of the city for 10,000 soldiers, with as many as 45,000 police officers on duty tomorrow night, as well as 20,000 private security guards.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the codename Operation Sentinelle\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"a military base\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"the outskirts\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"10,000 soldiers\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"as many as 45,000 police officers\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"duty\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"20,000 private security guards\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, French airspace within a 150km radius is set to be closed for the first time for the duration of the opening ceremony, which is expected to last three hours.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8375398598673065, \"rank\": 0.15428401926277047, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"a 150km radius\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"the duration\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"three hours\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are also anti-mine teams and anti-drone systems in place, as well as divers patrolling the Seine.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999976866319613, \"rank\": 2.3132581366354095e-06, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anti-mine teams\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"anti-drone systems\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"divers\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An estimated half-a-million Britons are expected to make the trip to Paris during the course of the Games, with Great Britain lending the support of 250 police officers, along with 50 police dogs, to boost the operation.\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1459, \"end\": 1464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0644224779468111e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999917623293242, \"rank\": 5.617761366743655e-06, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An estimated half-a-million Britons\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"the trip\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1455}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"250 police officers\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"50 police dogs\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"the operation\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 100,000 people are expected in the grandstands at tomorrow's ceremony, with a further 220,000 on raised walkways along a four-mile stretch.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More than 100,000 people\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"the grandstands\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"tomorrow's ceremony\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"raised walkways\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1734}, {\"ngram\": \"a four-mile stretch\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024: A Games on a spectacular scale - but is Paris ready to party?\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1818, \"end\": 1823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0644224779468111e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"A Games\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectacular scale\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is no stranger to terrorist attacks.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0644224779468111e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terrorist attacks\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2015, gunmen killed 130 people and wounded nearly 500 more in six different attacks.\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gunmen\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"130 people\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"six different attacks\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While no known threat has been identified in the lead-up, police this week rehearsed a bus hostage situation.\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no known threat\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead-up\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2036}, {\"ngram\": \"a bus hostage situation\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France's interior minister, Gerald Darmanin, said: \\\"We do not have any specific threats to the Olympic Games, either from French intelligence services or partner foreign services who are assisting us.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2083, \"end\": 2089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8095449220667932, \"rank\": 0.12209818979550571, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour